original_title: Pat McGee Band: Vintage Stages Live
overview: Enjoy a plethora of performances by the Pat McGee Band with this compilation that features a full-length concert, a mini acoustic set and numerous interviews. With their original blend of rock, jazz and blues, the innovative group has gained a loyal following since its inception in the mid-1990s. Songs include "Must Have Been Love," "You and I," "Annabel," "Haven't Seen for a While," "On Your Way Out of Here," "Girl from Athens" and many more.
title: Pat McGee Band: Vintage Stages Live
